snippet: Patrick Reed ran off five straight birdies in the middle of his round and finished with a bogey-free nine-under 63 to tie his career low at the Humana Challenge in La Quinta, Calif.
abstract: Patrick Reed ties his career low at the Humana Challenge in La Quinta, Calif, with bogey-free nine-under 63 in first round.
